{"tid":902532,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"女人過三十五就高齡產婦，男人根本都差唔多","createTime":"2018-11-15T01:27:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-15T06:01:13.000Z","uid":92123,"like":73,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d07fc1823d08f2af3989f2cdfbea67312ef68c2e","tid":902532,"uid":92123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T01:27:38.000Z","msg":"男人成日話梗係玩到四五十歲先搵個後生女結婚啦<br />\n岩架 如果唔生仔的話<br />\n如果係鐘意玩既話 就玩一世<br />\n唔好去到五十歲又話想成家立室想生仔<br />\n<br />\n女人過三十五就高齡產婦<br />\n根本男人過四十都叫高齡產夫<br />\n個仔二十歲 你就已經七老八十<br />\n有冇諗過個仔既感受？<br />\n你話你有錢到富豪級<br />\n咁你用錢塞畀下一代<br />\n唔洗咁多父愛<br />\n咁冇野好講<br />\n<br />\n如果係普遍家庭<br />\n男人成日想玩到年紀大先生仔<br />\n根本靜係諗自己<br />\n生仔唔係計生到個一刻就得<br />\n小朋友唔係公仔<br />\n係要包括陪佢玩同成長<br />\n<br />\n窮人生仔正仆街<br />\n中坑老野生仔一樣仆街！"},{"pid":"b0fa31b2313c39bd1d326bf9d95c8f0476ed08c2","tid":902532,"uid":123565,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T01:29:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c7d50fb2457a254b9b5d5b5df715f5dfad4216d","tid":902532,"uid":92123,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T01:32:24.000Z","msg":"又窮又老又係大陸娶個阿娟落黎香港生仔個d就罪加一等"},{"pid":"2a490098063b5f6fffad28dcf81d45382e10cc4a","tid":902532,"uid":9964,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T01:33:33.000Z","msg":"你知唔知高齡產婦依個term點解要出現？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59790b98c08cfc55bf6069956e88a9ccc0b2d307","tid":902532,"uid":92123,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T01:34:24.000Z","msg":"就算中產五十幾歲娶個二十幾既港女生仔都係自私！"},{"pid"